description.en: Folding@home is a project focused on disease research. The problems we're solving require so many computer calcul­ations - and we need your help to find the cures! Fight diseases Together with us.
description.ga_IE: Is tionscadal é Folding @ Home atá dírithe ar thaighde galair.Éilíonn na fadhbanna a theastaíonn uainn go leor ríomhaireachtaí ríomhaireachta - agus teastaíonn uait do chabhair chun na leigheasanna a aimsiú!Galair a chomhrac in éineacht linn.
